WEBVTT

00:03.131 --> 00:05.381
<b>Sasaki-san</b>

00:03.131 --> 00:05.381
<b>Wholesome Memorial Hospital</b>

00:05.671 --> 00:09.261
<b><i>It's that dreaded time of year again.</i></b>

00:10.131 --> 00:14.641
<b><i>Health checkups start to get scary 
around this age.</i></b>

00:15.011 --> 00:17.061
<b>Oho?</b>

00:17.061 --> 00:22.771
<b>The heck, man? You had nothing 
lower than a B in last year's checkup.</b>

00:22.771 --> 00:25.361
<b>Did you get any warnings, Suzuki?</b>

00:26.281 --> 00:28.441
<b>Uric acid and neutral fat levels.</b>

00:28.441 --> 00:30.781
<b>Tends to happen with salespeople.</b>

00:30.781 --> 00:35.161
<b>However! I'm a different man this year!</b>

00:35.161 --> 00:38.411
<b>Because ever since last year's checkups,</b>

00:38.411 --> 00:41.961
<b>I've been eating healthy lunches 
made by my dear Keiko-chan!</b>

00:43.211 --> 00:44.921
<b>Ta-da!</b>

00:45.921 --> 00:47.381
<b>That's a lot of food.</b>

00:47.921 --> 00:50.171
<b>You got it. I'll do my best!</b>

00:48.261 --> 00:50.171
<b>Hang in there</b>

00:52.301 --> 00:55.261
<b>Man, talk about love. This is pure love.</b>

00:55.261 --> 00:57.351
<b>Sure is!</b>

00:57.351 --> 00:59.851
<b>To live up to her love,</b>

00:59.851 --> 01:02.941
<b>I'm going to stop drinking and 
smoking until the health checkup.</b>

01:02.941 --> 01:04.611
<b>Time to eat.</b>

01:05.191 --> 01:07.441
<b>Drinking I get, but smoking, too?</b>

01:07.781 --> 01:13.031
<b>Aye. I want to live a long life 
together with Keiko-chan.</b>

01:19.701 --> 01:22.501
<b>I gotta chew my food well.</b>

01:23.211 --> 01:25.961
<b>Are you a regular smoker?</b>

01:23.211 --> 01:25.961
<b>Yes</b>

01:23.211 --> 01:25.961
<b>No</b>

01:28.711 --> 01:31.011
<b>That'll be 1,160 yen.</b>

01:31.011 --> 01:31.921
<b>Right.</b>

01:36.761 --> 01:38.851
<b>Here's your change and receipt.</b>

01:40.471 --> 01:42.231
<b>Also, here.</b>

01:42.601 --> 01:46.811
<b>There's a new brand of non-alcoholic 
beer out with a promotional discount.</b>

01:46.811 --> 01:47.901
<b>Use it, if you'd like.</b>

01:47.901 --> 01:50.481
<b>Oh, thank you.</b>

01:50.861 --> 01:53.451
<b>I have a health checkup coming up soon,</b>

01:53.451 --> 01:56.621
<b>so I've been thinking about switching 
to non-alcoholic drinks for a bit.</b>

01:56.621 --> 01:57.991
<b>This will help.</b>

01:57.991 --> 01:59.911
<b><i>Oh?</i></b>

03:45.141 --> 03:46.891
<b>Good evening, Tayama-san.</b>

03:46.891 --> 03:51.401
<b>Hey, look who's here to smoke even 
though he has a health checkup soon.</b>

03:51.401 --> 03:51.901
<b>Huh?</b>

03:52.151 --> 03:54.691
<b>H-How do you know about that?</b>

03:56.241 --> 03:58.321
<b>Yamada-san told you?</b>

03:58.321 --> 04:01.781
<b>Yeah, yeah, I heard from Yamada-san.</b>

04:01.781 --> 04:03.281
<b><i>Sa-slow-ki.</i></b>

04:04.081 --> 04:07.451
<b>Yeah, it's real soon.</b>

04:07.451 --> 04:10.921
<b>I've reduced my daily count, okay?</b>

04:11.631 --> 04:12.921
<b>Pardon me.</b>

04:12.921 --> 04:16.761
<b>Reduced by what, one or two at most?</b>

04:17.511 --> 04:19.301
<b>Well... yes.</b>

04:25.971 --> 04:29.641
<b>Do supermarket employees 
get health checkups, too?</b>

04:29.641 --> 04:33.441
<b>Yeah. Ours will probably 
also come up pretty soon.</b>

04:34.401 --> 04:38.821
<b>Will you cut down before that too, then?</b>

04:38.821 --> 04:40.821
<b>Cut down...</b>

04:41.951 --> 04:43.571
<b>fl</b>

04:41.951 --> 04:43.571
<b>ab...</b>

04:43.871 --> 04:45.911
<b><i>I'll only drink one spoonful of the broth.</i></b>

04:47.081 --> 04:47.911
<b>Of course.</b>

04:47.911 --> 04:49.251
<b>Wow!</b>

04:49.911 --> 04:52.581
<b>Health is wealth, after all.</b>

04:52.581 --> 04:55.251
<b>If we don't take care of our health, 
we won't be able to work.</b>

04:55.251 --> 04:58.591
<b>Way to go. You're so cool, Tayama-san.</b>

04:59.171 --> 05:02.341
<b>On the other hand, 
look at me and my pathetic self.</b>

05:03.091 --> 05:06.971
<b>I'm trying stopgap measures 
instead of just quitting beer for a while.</b>

05:06.971 --> 05:10.731
<b>And yet you've got a lotta food today.</b>

05:10.731 --> 05:16.231
<b>Oh, the doctors tell me every year 
to gain some weight.</b>

05:17.691 --> 05:21.451
<b>But I have a hard time keeping it on.</b>

05:21.451 --> 05:25.531
<b>Wish I could put on weight more easily.</b>

05:24.951 --> 05:25.531
<b>Yoink.</b>

05:26.621 --> 05:27.871
<b>Wh-What was that for?</b>

05:27.871 --> 05:30.411
<b>You really are all skin and bones.</b>

05:30.411 --> 05:32.411
<b>T-Tayama-san?</b>

05:32.411 --> 05:36.751
<b>Our deli section has the good stuff. 
Eat lots of it and gain weight.</b>

05:37.381 --> 05:39.671
<b>O-Okay, thanks.</b>

05:40.841 --> 05:41.801
<b>Well...</b>

05:42.091 --> 05:45.141
<b>I haven't been able to quit 
the single most harmful thing,</b>

05:45.141 --> 05:47.471
<b>so everything might as well be stopgap.</b>

05:47.471 --> 05:49.681
<b>Well, duh.</b>

05:51.181 --> 05:54.941
<b>But what if the doctors 
tell you to quit smoking?</b>

05:55.271 --> 05:57.111
<b>Would you quit?</b>

05:57.111 --> 05:57.861
<b>Huh?</b>

06:00.321 --> 06:02.741
<b>Well, uh...</b>

06:03.451 --> 06:05.201
<b>If I have to quit,</b>

06:05.201 --> 06:08.161
<b>that might be a problem.</b>

06:09.201 --> 06:10.451
<b>After all,</b>

06:11.451 --> 06:13.081
<b>the chief—</b>

06:11.451 --> 06:13.081
<b>Your boss...</b>

06:14.001 --> 06:15.871
<b>will still be hurling abuses at you.</b>

06:17.461 --> 06:20.461
<b>Yeah, and I don't think 
I'd be able to take it.</b>

06:21.551 --> 06:24.971
<b>Yeah, I might have 
a hard time quitting, too.</b>

06:24.971 --> 06:28.101
<b>I'd be done for if that happened.</b>

06:30.971 --> 06:32.351
<b>It's all good.</b>

06:33.981 --> 06:37.601
<b>There. Now you have an invincible body.</b>

06:44.321 --> 06:45.531
<b>Thanks.</b>

06:47.111 --> 06:51.741
<b><i>I feel like I've been overthinking 
all this cutting-down nonsense.</i></b>

06:51.741 --> 06:54.461
<b><i>I've come back to my senses now,</i></b>

06:55.541 --> 06:57.501
<b><i>and it's all thanks to Tayama-san...</i></b>

06:59.541 --> 07:02.421
<b><i>But what if the doctors 
tell you to quit smoking?</i></b>

07:07.841 --> 07:11.471
<b><i>I'd have to... of course.</i></b>

07:24.401 --> 07:26.401
<b>Wholesome Memorial Hospital</b>

07:24.401 --> 07:26.401
<b>Chill Pharmacy</b>

07:52.431 --> 07:54.431
<b>Sasaki-san</b>

07:52.431 --> 07:54.431
<b>Private</b>

07:52.431 --> 07:54.431
<b>Results Enclosed</b>

07:52.431 --> 07:54.431
<b>Wholesome Memorial Hospital</b>

07:54.431 --> 07:56.431
<b>Yahoo!</b>

07:56.731 --> 08:00.981
<b>My uric acid and neutral fats 
are within normal levels! I got an A!</b>

08:01.401 --> 08:04.441
<b>Wait, why have I gained weight 
since last year, though?</b>

08:04.821 --> 08:08.361
<b>Whatever! I need to tell Keiko-chan!</b>

08:08.031 --> 08:09.201
<b></b>Very Healthy

08:08.361 --> 08:09.281
<b>Snappity snap.</b>

08:09.281 --> 08:11.701
<b>Tell me how yours came out later!</b>

08:11.701 --> 08:13.831
<b>I'm going for a smoke!</b>

08:21.331 --> 08:23.381
<b>What's up?</b>

08:23.381 --> 08:25.341
<b>How'd your checkup go?</b>

08:29.221 --> 08:31.801
<b>What's wrong? Did your shitty boss 
do something again?</b>

08:32.471 --> 08:36.721
<b>No. It's my body that's shitty.</b>

08:36.721 --> 08:37.521
<b>Wha?</b>

08:38.101 --> 08:39.891
<b>Tayama-san, uh...</b>

08:41.061 --> 08:44.571
<b>Smoking really is bad for you, huh?</b>

08:50.151 --> 08:54.451
<b>Sasaki-kun's checkup told him 
to get scanned and treated?</b>

08:54.451 --> 08:55.371
<b>For his lungs?</b>

08:55.871 --> 08:57.661
<b>I'm sorry for his loss.</b>

08:58.121 --> 09:00.621
<b>So he's going to quit smoking.</b>

09:00.621 --> 09:02.081
<b>Of course he would.</b>

09:04.171 --> 09:06.131
<b>What, Yamada?</b>

09:06.881 --> 09:10.881
<b>He won't have a reason 
to show up back there anymore.</b>

09:13.431 --> 09:14.431
<b>Yamada.</b>

09:14.971 --> 09:18.891
<b>If Sasaki-kun found out that someone 
had a surprising side to them,</b>

09:19.221 --> 09:21.891
<b>is he the kind of guy who 
wouldn't be able to accept it?</b>

09:21.891 --> 09:24.061
<b>He's not like that.</b>

09:24.061 --> 09:25.731
<b>Then all you need to say is,</b>

09:25.731 --> 09:28.861
<b>"It's actually me you always 
see at register two."</b>

09:29.481 --> 09:31.901
<b>Then you won't need a pretext 
to see each other.</b>

09:33.571 --> 09:34.411
<b>Well...</b>

09:34.741 --> 09:38.161
<b>His ideal image of Yamada-san 
the goddess will crumble to dust,</b>

09:38.161 --> 09:41.201
<b>but only because he'll start 
seeing you for who you are.</b>

09:43.671 --> 09:47.461
<b>Hey, Yamada? Are you listenin' to me?</b>

09:46.251 --> 09:47.961
<b>Excuse me.</b>

09:47.461 --> 09:49.631
<b>Yes, how may I help you?</b>

09:49.631 --> 09:51.721
<b>I was hoping to get this wrapped.</b>

09:51.721 --> 09:53.301
<b>Of course. Right away.</b>

09:57.721 --> 09:59.891
<b><i>I know that.</i></b>

10:01.391 --> 10:02.641
<b><i>So why...</i></b>

10:06.231 --> 10:08.271
<b><i>Why am I freaking out?</i></b>

10:09.151 --> 10:11.151
<b>24-Hour</b>

10:09.151 --> 10:11.151
<b>Supermarket S</b>

10:14.151 --> 10:16.951
<b><i>I finally get a day off.</i></b>

10:16.951 --> 10:19.241
<b><i>Guess I'll go to the hospital tomorrow.</i></b>

10:24.371 --> 10:26.881
<b><i>I'll need to stop by and say 
goodbye sometime, too.</i></b>

10:31.961 --> 10:33.761
<b>T... Tayama-san?!</b>

10:33.761 --> 10:35.551
<b>Do you have plans now?</b>

10:35.551 --> 10:37.931
<b>Huh? No, nothing.</b>

10:37.931 --> 10:39.761
<b>Come with me, then.</b>

10:47.191 --> 10:48.061
<b>Oh.</b>

10:50.361 --> 10:53.441
<b>Go ahead and smoke, Tayama-san.</b>

10:53.691 --> 10:59.161
<b>I'd like to chew on this and smoke 
vicariously through you one last time.</b>

10:59.161 --> 11:00.831
<b>Oh, yeah?</b>

11:09.671 --> 11:12.381
<b>Are you really gonna be able 
to quit like that?</b>

11:13.051 --> 11:14.971
<b>I'm not very confident.</b>

11:15.341 --> 11:16.761
<b>Do you think I can?</b>

11:17.931 --> 11:19.931
<b>Don't ask me.</b>

11:23.221 --> 11:24.601
<b>Tayama-san.</b>

11:26.851 --> 11:30.901
<b>Thanks for inviting me 
back here back then.</b>

11:32.191 --> 11:36.651
<b>We probably won't have the chance 
to talk like this anymore,</b>

11:37.401 --> 11:40.621
<b>but if you happen 
to see me in the store...</b>

11:41.781 --> 11:42.991
<b>Don't say any more.</b>

11:44.371 --> 11:48.791
<b>Sasaki-san, I need to tell you something.</b>

11:53.671 --> 11:54.671
<b>Oh, sorry.</b>

11:54.671 --> 11:55.461
<b>Take it.</b>

11:55.461 --> 11:57.011
<b>O-Okay.</b>

11:58.841 --> 12:01.341
<b>Hello? Sasaki here.</b>

12:01.341 --> 12:02.051
<b>Yes.</b>

12:02.511 --> 12:04.721
<b>Right, my checkup results?</b>

12:05.181 --> 12:08.271
<b>I was thinking of going 
for scans tomorrow.</b>

12:08.641 --> 12:09.271
<b>Huh?</b>

12:09.771 --> 12:10.521
<b>What?</b>

12:12.311 --> 12:14.611
<b>Okay, I understand.</b>

12:15.901 --> 12:17.281
<b>Goodbye.</b>

12:29.661 --> 12:31.581
<b>It was a misdiagnosis.</b>

12:33.171 --> 12:37.301
<b>Apparently, my organs 
are very healthy for my age.</b>

12:40.801 --> 12:42.261
<b>I'm sorry!</b>

12:43.511 --> 12:45.181
<b>I'm happy for you!</b>

12:45.681 --> 12:47.851
<b>Sorry! I'm sorry, Tayama-san!</b>

12:47.851 --> 12:49.941
<b>Boy, am I glad to hear it.</b>

12:49.181 --> 12:51.311
<b>I made you worry for nothing!</b>

12:49.941 --> 12:52.021
<b>So very glad.</b>

12:51.311 --> 12:53.191
<b>I'm really sorry.</b>

12:52.401 --> 12:54.021
<b>Good for you.</b>

12:54.521 --> 12:56.821
<b>I'm so glad, though.</b>

12:57.821 --> 13:01.911
<b>I can keep smoking with you, huh?</b>

13:06.911 --> 13:11.251
<b>Oh, right. You said you wanted 
to tell me something.</b>

13:11.251 --> 13:12.671
<b>Sorry I cut you off.</b>

13:13.291 --> 13:14.961
<b>Could you tell me now?</b>

13:23.091 --> 13:24.141
<b>It's okay.</b>

13:26.011 --> 13:27.761
<b>It doesn't have to be now.</b>

13:29.521 --> 13:30.731
<b>So...</b>

13:32.481 --> 13:34.771
<b>Let's keep smoking together.</b>

13:36.611 --> 13:40.361
<b>Don't think I'm letting you off easy 
for winding me up like that, though.</b>

13:40.361 --> 13:43.661
<b>Y-Yeah, I'm sorry about that.</b>

13:43.661 --> 13:47.031
<b>But I do appreciate your concern.</b>

13:47.531 --> 13:48.331
<b>Hmph.</b>

13:50.071 --> 13:53.701
<b>Translation: Sriram Gurunathan</b>

13:54.201 --> 13:57.831
<b>Editing & Typesetting: Geoff Mazzolini
Subtitle Timing: Krzysztof Kunc</b>

13:58.541 --> 14:01.791
<b>Quality Check: Zachary Carlysle
Translation Check: Sho Stifler</b>
